desc: Our goal is to offer the fastest and most reliable Ethernet cables, connecting hardware, tools, and low voltage supplies directly to you. Shop with us today!

layout.text: "My company, SASGUARD Computing LLC, has used trueCABLE since we started back in 2018 around Dec. We have had many other cable companies that used CCA (Copper-clad aluminium wire) and we’ve had issues with PoE and other issues with the wiring to the point where we had to re-run cables. We found TrueCable and gave it a shot and it just became our staple. It’s highly reliable. Me and my technicians are always confident with our runs and network environment because of the quality."
